## 6. Zero Trust Checklist (self-verify before output)

- [ ] No `net/http`, `database/sql`, `gin` import in any `domain/` file
- [ ] No anemic model — business rules are methods on the aggregate, not in the use case
- [ ] Every method signature starts with `ctx context.Context`
- [ ] Every error is wrapped with `fmt.Errorf("...: %w", err)`
- [ ] No `panic()` or `log.Fatal()` outside `main()`
- [ ] No `time.Now()` — `Clock` interface injected
- [ ] No `time.Sleep()` in any test file
- [ ] No package-level variables for godog state
- [ ] All monetary/measurement values are `int64` with correct suffix
- [ ] `go test -race ./...` is GREEN before task is declared complete
